Which choice is true? Answer choices: (A) 02/08/2018, (B) 10/22/2018, (C) 01/08/2019, (D) 01/01/2019, (E) 01/08/2043, (F) 01/08/1960.
chain: 1. The first Monday of 2019 was on January 7th. 2. Adding 24 hours to January 7th, we get January 8th. 3. Therefore, the date 24 hours later in MM/DD/YYYY format is 01/08/2019. 4. The correct answer choice is (C) 01/08/2019.
